<text top="806" left="539" width="2" height="8" font="11"> </text>
<text top="74" left="142" width="10" height="9" font="1">4. </text>
<text top="74" left="170" width="41" height="9" font="6"><i>Welcomes</i></text>
<text top="74" left="211" width="274" height="9" font="1"> the holding on 14 June 2018 of the intersessional workshop on the </text>
<text top="86" left="113" width="371" height="9" font="1">right to peace, at which participants discussed the implementation of the Declaration on the </text>
<text top="98" left="113" width="125" height="9" font="1">Right to Peace, and takes note</text>
<text top="98" left="238" width="2" height="9" font="6"><i> </i></text>
<text top="98" left="241" width="243" height="9" font="1">of the summary report thereon of the United Nations  High </text>
